# âš›Electronic Structure Analysis Scripts

![license](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue.svg)
![python](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.x-blue.svg)

Automated extraction of **band gap**, **valence/conduction band edges**, and **work function** from electronic structure simulation outputs.

---

## Folder Contents

| Script | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `band_gap_parser.py` | Extract band gap and band edge data from `.out` files |
| `work_function_parser.py` | Extract work function and electrostatic potential info from `POTC` files |

---

